text: Willelm kyng gret Willelm bisceop and swegn scyrgerefan and ealle mine þegna for East seaxan freondlice.
And ic kyðe eow þæt ic habbe geunnen Deormanne minan mon þa hide landes æt Gyddes dune þe hi of geryden wæs.
And ic nelle geþolian frencisan ne engliscan þæt him æt ænigan þingan misbeode.
